        <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;flowchart TD\n    subgraph T1 [Tier 1: Ingestion &amp; Feature Extraction]\n        direction LR\n        Webcam[Webcam Video Feed] --&gt; Vision[Vision Backend&lt;br/&gt;Producer Process]\n        Jarvis[JARVIS Orchestrator &amp; GUI] -.-&gt; Vision\n        Vision --&gt; MP[MediaPipe Holistic&lt;br/&gt;Single-Pass]\n    end\n\n    subgraph T2 [Tier 2: Concurrency &amp; Synchronization]\n        RAM[(Zero-Copy Shared Memory)]\n    end\n\n    subgraph T3 [Tier 3: Parallel Processing Pipelines]\n        direction LR\n        subgraph HCI [HCI Controller]\n            direction TB\n            HCI_Read[Reads Array] --&gt; RH[Right Hand Landmarks]\n            RH --&gt; Geo[Geometric Heuristics]\n            Geo --&gt; Filter[One Euro Filter &amp; Sigmoid]\n            Filter --&gt; OS[PyAutoGUI OS Integration]\n        end\n        subgraph ISL [ISL Controller]\n            direction TB\n            ISL_Read[Reads Array] --&gt; Vector[Upper-Body Spatial Vector]\n            Vector --&gt; Norm[Shoulder-Invariant Normalization]\n            Norm --&gt; Window[30-Frame Temporal Window]\n            Window --&gt; LSTM[LSTM Network]\n            LSTM --&gt; Debounce[Debouncing]\n        end\n    end\n\n    subgraph T4 [Tier 4: Terminal Output]\n        Out1[Deterministic OS Actions]\n        Out2[Semantic Translation &amp; TTS]\n    end\n\n    MP -- Writes Array --&gt; RAM\n    RAM -- Reads Array --&gt; HCI_Read\n    RAM -- Reads Array --&gt; ISL_Read\n    OS --&gt; Out1\n    Debounce --&gt; Out2\n\n    style Jarvis fill:#eff6ff,stroke:#333\n    style Vision fill:#faf5ff,stroke:#333\n    style MP fill:#faf5ff,stroke:#333\n    style HCI fill:#f0fdf4,stroke:#333\n    style ISL fill:#fef2f2,stroke:#333\n    style RAM fill:#f9f9f9,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;config&quot;: null&#xa;}" id="3xsYKmnh_5ejZav0TJ8w-6">
